{"word":"G4517 - ῥώννυμι - rhṓnnymi - hrone'-noo-mee - Farewell","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥώννυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">rhṓnnymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hrone'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Farewell</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுகமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to make strong, to strengthen;"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Prolonged from <b>&#x03C1;&#x0314;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> <b>rho&#x0304;omai</b> (to <i>dart</i>; probably akin to <a href=\"#/G4506 - ῥύομαι - rhýomai - rhoo'-om-ahee/4506\">G4506</a>); to <i>strengthen</i>, that is, (imperative passive) <i>have health</i> (as parting exclamation, <i>good bye</i>): - farewell.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}